    "body": "Confirming that verification is _totally_ broken right now.\r\n\r\nTo get it working we need a few things:\r\n1. Storing compiler settings (version + optimizer runs) per file in ethers-solc, WIP here: https://github.com/gakonst/ethers-rs/pull/755\r\n1. Supporting flattening contract source (needs to follow remappings / imports etc.) in ethers-solc.\r\n1. Integrating that in `verify`, WIP here: https://github.com/gakonst/foundry/pull/354\r\n1. Integrating the `verify` command's components in `create --verify`\r\n\r\nWe should also consider how to approach multi file verification. @paulrberg had some work on this https://github.com/paulrberg/multisol/",
